<item>
            <title>[LU-2922] update lustre-ldiskfs.spec.in e2fsprogs Requires: line</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2922</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;lustre-ldiskfs currently requires e2fsprogs-1.41.12.2.ora1, but there have been a number of bug fixes that should be used by Lustre 2.x users.  Update the .spec file to depend on a newer e2fsprogs-1.42.6.wc2 release.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This also means that the current 1.42.6.wc2 builds should be available from the downloads.whamcloud.com/public/e2fsprogs site.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="17788">LU-2922</key>
