                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="54027" author="yujian" created="Thu, 14 Mar 2013 12:51:17 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;We also need a patch to fix lustre/ChangeLog to reference the newer e2fsprogs.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Patch for master branch: &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/5718&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/5718&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hello, Oleg, I did not see a Lustre 2.1.5 entry in lustre/ChangeLog on b2_1 branch. Could you please add one and recommend the e2fsprogs version 1.42.6.wc2? Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="54026" author="adilger" created="Thu, 14 Mar 2013 12:47:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We also need a patch to fix lustre/ChangeLog to reference the newer e2fsprogs.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="53653" author="pjones" created="Sat, 9 Mar 2013 20:16:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Landed for 2.1.5 and 2.4&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="53507" author="mdiep" created="Thu, 7 Mar 2013 01:48:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Done&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="53505" author="yujian" created="Thu, 7 Mar 2013 01:10:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Minh,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Could you please upload the e2fsprogs-1.42.6.wc2 packages to &lt;a href=&quot;http://downloads.whamcloud.com/public/e2fsprogs/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://downloads.whamcloud.com/public/e2fsprogs/&lt;/a&gt; ? Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="53504" author="yujian" created="Thu, 7 Mar 2013 01:03:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Oleg,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;After the patch for Lustre master branch passes review and test, could you please cherry-pick it to Lustre b2_1 branch? Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="53503" author="yujian" created="Thu, 7 Mar 2013 00:58:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Andreas,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I did not find e2fsprogs-1.42.6.wc2 on &lt;a href=&quot;http://downloads.whamcloud.com/public/e2fsprogs/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://downloads.whamcloud.com/public/e2fsprogs/&lt;/a&gt;. Do you know who I can ask for help to upload the packages?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="53502" author="yujian" created="Thu, 7 Mar 2013 00:48:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch for Lustre master branch is in &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/5623&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/5623&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
